title: Discovery Channel Whats That About Getting Clean Xvid AC3
description:
It can be hard for some people to get up out of bed, but the process of the morning washing ritual can be a real eye-opener.

The shower, soap, razors, even the toilet are all the result of a lengthy evolutionary process in personal hygiene.

Find out why humankind added chalk to toothpaste, aluminum to antiperspirant, and how baby nappies were made even more absorbent because of an astronaut&#039;s space suit.
